{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Mimics Pro Tools' "Display Timeline Selection End" behavior.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Priority: Razor Edit > Time Selection > Item Selection.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab View scrolls to the end of the active selection without changing zoom level or play/edit cursor.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Useful for navigating to timeline boundaries in a non-destructive way.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice.\line hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Designed for fast, keyboard-light workflows.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Integrates with Razor Edit regions when available.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Uses SWS extension APIs where available.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 References:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER ReaScript API (Lua)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab SWS Extension API\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab This is a 0.1 beta release for internal testing.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Single item = normal toggle. Multiple items:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab mixed mute states -> unify to UNMUTE\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab uniform state -> toggle all\sa180\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Pro Tools-style "Paste Special: Repeat to Fill Selection"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Stage whole block at a far "staging area", then move once into Razor.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab No system Auto-Crossfade; ALL fades are applied manually.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab JOIN crossfades between repeated tiles (after moving into target we verify/repair).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Boundary crossfades ONLY when edge-to-edge, and without moving any item:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Left boundary: extend LEFT neighbor's right edge (no move).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Right boundary: extend LAST-IN-AREA item's right edge (no move).\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Items only; envelopes not supported yet (Razor contains envelope -> abort).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Restores original item/track selection.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Known issues:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab CF_UNIT="grid" is still inaccurate/experimental; use seconds/frames for reliable results.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab When requested JOIN is much larger than the tile length, the script auto-adjusts JOIN to a fraction of the tile for stability. In certain source/material combinations this may still yield visually irregular overlaps. Workarounds: lower CF_VALUE or copy a longer source tile.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Reference: MRX_PasteItemToFill_Items_and_EnvelopeLanes.lua\par}
}

