{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Emulates Pro Tools' "Trim Clip to File Boundaries" behavior.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Extends both left and right edges of selected item(s) based on neighboring items.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Falls back to full file start/end if no neighbors exist.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Always respects file content bounds, avoiding empty/unrecorded areas.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u55357 ?\u56481 ? Ideal for reclaiming full usable media without overshooting source boundaries.\line Integrates well with hsuanice's Pro Tools-style editing workflow.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice.\line hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Designed for fast, keyboard-light workflows.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 References:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER ReaScript API (Lua)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
}

