{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Emulates Pro Tools' "Trim Clip End to File End" behavior.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Extends the right edge of selected item(s) to the next item's start, or to the source media end.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Prevents extending into unrecorded/empty content area.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Automatically respects source limits and adjusts for playrate and offset.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u55357 ?\u56481 ? Ideal for reclaiming usable audio content without overshooting media length. Integrates well with hsuanice's Pro Tools-style timeline workflows.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Designed for fast, keyboard-light workflows.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 References:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER ReaScript API (Lua)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab This is a 0.1 beta release for internal testing.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Emulates Pro Tools' "Trim Clip Start to File Start" behavior.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Extends the left edge of selected item(s) up to the previous item's end, or to the source media start.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Prevents revealing beyond recorded content.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Keeps normal left-edge reveal behavior when there is available headroom.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If a left blank loop was created by "SWS/AW: Trim selected items to fill selection", the loop is collapsed in a content-preserving way (push start right by overshoot, shorten length, zero offset).\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
